---
title: Honey-Broiled Feta with Turkish Chickpeas and Spinach on Couscous
description: Drizzle feta with sweet, sticky honey and broil until golden. Sprinkle it over chickpeas braised in a Turkish-style tomato stew. Served it all over a herby couscous to soak up the bold and satisfying flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/feta-grille-au-miel-d0f7dda3.jpg
